snippet.title: SWARM 2 - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
SWARM 2, the highly anticipated sequel to VR’s #1-rated action game, is an electrifying rogue-like shooter.  Coming March 7th 2023 to Meta Quest 2 + Quest 3.

With epic new environments, intoxicating rogue-like progression, and globally competitive leaderboards where "You feel like SPIDER-MAN WITH GUNS”. 

Pre-order now to receive a 12% discount and  a Legendary ‘Crimson Strike’ skin for Marv’s revolver!
https://www.meta.com/en-us/experiences/5791805387504648/

#swarm2VR
